mul_apply:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃r » -/
theorem mul_apply (e₁ e₂ : «expr ≃r » r r) (x : α) : (e₁ * e₂) x = e₁ (e₂ x) :=
  rfl
#align mul_apply mul_apply
inv_apply_self:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃r » -/
@[simp]
theorem inv_apply_self (e : «expr ≃r » r r) (x) : e⁻¹ (e x) = x :=
  e.symm_apply_apply x
#align inv_apply_self inv_apply_self

coe_mul:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃r » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⇑ » -/

theorem coe_mul (e₁ e₂ : «expr ≃r » r r) : «expr⇑ » (e₁ * e₂) = e₁ ∘ e₂ :=
  rfl

apply_inv_self:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃r » -/
@[simp]
theorem apply_inv_self (e : «expr ≃r » r r) (x) : e (e⁻¹ x) = x :=
  e.apply_symm_apply x
#align apply_inv_self apply_inv_self
